{
  "stem": "10859.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the partisans, I have to tell you, we did a lot of damage and destroyed a lot of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We used to go and put up on the rails ammunition, bombs which blew up the rails.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they used to collapse over there where they used to go and travel soldiers to the front, or ammunition, or clothes, or food, whatever-- we used to destroy this on the way.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We used to do to them so much damage-- unbelievable, the, the partisans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, what it called Volhynia Gubernia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Ukrainian, Volhynia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Volhynia was like, here, a state.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not a big state like California, but a small state which has only 5,000 people, or 6,000 people there [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's Volhynia Gubernia, and that's what we were over there with the-- with the partisans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Food, we had plenty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no shortage of food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we used to go in a village and just clean them up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They didn't play with them, Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- and the fight, of course, was with the Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not so much with, with the Polish people like with the Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was constantly fights and fights and fights.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then to make it a little bit the, the story shorter, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] only one thing we felt good, at least we felt like we are something, human beings.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We can take revenge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We can fight, not just go to the grave and be shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- in the spring of 1944, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we were already, at that time-- I in the, the other people from the-- when we got out from the-- we were liberated by the-- by the Russian Army, you know?",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were free.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
